      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E92 M3 powered by the high-revving S65 4.0L V8, featuring eight individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. This specimen retains exceptional mechanical integrity, with recent preventative maintenance including rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damping Control (EDC) and an M Variable Differential Lock for superior lateral dynamics. Power is delivered through a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox, and the factory CFRP roof panel ensures a reduced polar moment of inertia. A technically sound example with a documented service history, optimized for performance-oriented ownership.",
